  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">We have recast certain prior period amounts to conform to the way we internally manage and monitor our business.</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <hr style="page-break-after:always;">
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">MICROSOFT CORPORATION</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">FOURTH QUARTER FINANCIAL HIGHLIGHTS</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">All growth comparisons relate to the corresponding period in the last fiscal year.</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">SUMMARY</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Revenue increased $4.3 billion or 8% driven by growth in Intelligent Cloud and Productivity and Business Processes, offset in part by a decline in More Personal Computing. Intelligent Cloud revenue increased driven by Azure and other cloud services. Productivity and Business Processes revenue increased driven by Office 365 Commercial. More Personal Computing revenue decreased driven by Devices and Windows, offset in part by Search and news advertising.</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Cost of revenue increased $366 million or 2% driven by growth in Microsoft Cloud, offset in part by a reduction in depreciation expense due to the change in accounting estimate for the useful lives of our server and network equipment and a decline in Devices.</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Gross margin increased $4.0 billion or 11% driven by growth in Intelligent Cloud and Productivity and Business Processes and the change in accounting estimate.</font><font style="color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Gross margin percentage increased. Excluding the impact of the change in accounting estimate, gross margin percentage increased slightly driven by improvements in Productivity and Business Processes and sales mix shift, offset in part by declines in Intelligent Cloud. </font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:6.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Microsoft Cloud gross margin percentage increased 3 points to 72%. Excluding the impact of the change in accounting estimate, Microsoft Cloud gross margin percentage increased slightly driven by improvement in Office 365 Commercial, offset in part by lower Azure and other cloud services margin.</font></div></div>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <hr style="page-break-after:always;">
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Operating expenses increased $238 million or 2% driven by a charge related to a non-public preliminary draft decision provided by the Irish Data Protection Commission (the &#x201c;IDPC matter&#x201d;).</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Operating income increased $3.7 billion or 18% driven by growth in Productivity and Business Processes and Intelligent Cloud and the change in accounting estimate.</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Revenue, gross margin, and operating income included an unfavorable foreign currency impact of 2%, 2%, and 3%, respectively.</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">SEGMENT INFORMATION</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;font-style:italic;min-width:fit-content;">Productivity and Business Processes</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Revenue increased $1.7 billion or 10%.</font></p>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Office Commercial products and cloud services revenue increased $1.2 billion or 12%. Office 365 Commercial revenue grew 15% with seat growth of 11%, driven by small and medium business and frontline worker offerings, as well as growth in revenue per user. Office Commercial products revenue declined 20% driven by continued customer shift to cloud offerings.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Office Consumer products and cloud services revenue increased $54 million or 3%. Microsoft 365 Consumer subscribers grew 12% to 67.0 million.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Dynamics products and cloud services revenue increased $236 million or 19% driven by Dynamics 365 growth of 26%.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">LinkedIn revenue increased $197 million or 5% driven by growth in Talent Solutions, offset in part by a decline in Marketing Solutions.</font></div></div>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Operating income increased $1.8 billion or 25%.</font></p>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Gross margin increased $1.8 billion or 14% driven by growth in Office 365 Commercial. Gross margin percentage increased. Excluding the impact of the change in accounting estimate, gross margin percentage increased 1 point driven by improvement in Office 365 Commercial.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Operating expenses decreased slightly primarily driven by declines in LinkedIn and Office marketing, offset in part by a charge related to the IDPC matter. </font></div></div>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Revenue, gross margin, and operating income included an unfavorable foreign currency impact of 2%, 2%, and 4%, respectively.</font><font style="color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;font-style:italic;min-width:fit-content;">Intelligent Cloud</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Revenue increased $3.2 billion or 15%.</font></p>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Server products and cloud services revenue increased $3.1 billion or 17% driven by Azure and other cloud services. Azure and other cloud services revenue grew 26% driven by growth in our consumption-based services. Server products revenue decreased 1%.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:6.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Enterprise Services revenue increased $75 million or 4% driven by growth in Enterprise Support Services, offset in part by a decline in Industry Solutions (formerly Microsoft Consulting Services).</font></div></div>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Operating income increased $1.7 billion or 20%.</font><font style="color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Gross margin increased $2.3 billion or 16% driven by growth in Azure and other cloud services and the change in accounting estimate. Gross margin percentage increased slightly. Excluding the impact of the change in accounting estimate, gross margin percentage decreased 2 points driven by sales mix shift to Azure and other cloud services and lower Azure and other cloud services margin.</font></div></div>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <hr style="page-break-after:always;">
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Operating expenses increased $570 million or 10% primarily driven by a charge related to the IDPC matter. </font></div></div>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Revenue and operating income both included an unfavorable foreign currency impact of 2%.</font><font style="color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;font-style:italic;min-width:fit-content;">More Personal Computing</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Revenue decreased $556 million or 4%.</font><font style="color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Windows revenue decreased $337 million or 5% driven by a decrease in Windows OEM. Windows OEM revenue decreased 12% primarily driven by continued PC market weakness, offset in part by roughly 7 points of benefit from early back-to-school inventory builds. Windows Commercial products and cloud services revenue increased 2% driven by demand for Microsoft 365.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Devices revenue decreased $339 million or 20%.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Search and news advertising revenue increased $86 million or 3%. Search and news advertising revenue excluding traffic acquisition costs increased 8% driven by higher search volume, as the benefit from the Xandr acquisition was more than offset by the impact from third-party partnerships.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Gaming revenue increased $36 million or 1% driven by growth in Xbox content and services, offset in part by a decline in Xbox hardware. Xbox content and services revenue increased 5% driven by growth in third-party content and Xbox Game Pass. Xbox hardware revenue decreased 13% driven by lower volume of consoles sold. </font></div></div>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Operating income increased $186 million or 4%.</font></p>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Gross margin decreased $124 million or 2% driven by a decline in Windows, offset in part by growth in Gaming. Gross margin percentage increased driven by sales mix shift to higher margin businesses.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Operating expenses decreased $310 million or 9% driven by declines in Devices and Windows, offset in part by a charge related to the IDPC matter.</font></div></div>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Gross margin and operating income both included an unfavorable foreign currency impact of 2%.</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">OPERATING EXPENSES</font></p>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Research and development expenses decreased $110 million or 2% driven by a decline in Devices, offset in part by investments in LinkedIn.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Sales and marketing expenses decreased $100 million or 2% primarily driven by declines in Windows, LinkedIn, and Devices advertising.</font></div></div>
  <div style="margin-left:3.333%;text-indent:0.0%;display:flex;margin-top:12.0pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.0pt;min-width:3.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;text-indent:0;display:inline-flex;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;justify-content:flex-start;min-width:3.447919145106397%;">&#x2022;</font><div style="display:inline;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">General and administrative expenses increased $448 million or 26% driven by a charge related to the IDPC matter. </font></div></div>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">OTHER INCOME (EXPENSE), NET</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Other income (expense), net was $473 million driven by interest and dividends income, offset in part by interest expense.</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">INCOME TAXES</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">The current quarter effective tax rate was 19% compared to 18% in the prior year. The increase in our effective tax rate was primarily due to a decrease in tax benefits relating to stock-based compensation.</font><font style="color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <hr style="page-break-after:always;">
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">REMAINING PERFORMANCE OBLIGATIONS</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:12.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:rgba(102,102,102,1);white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:normal;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">Revenue allocated to remaining performance obligations, which includes unearned revenue and amounts that will be invoiced and recognized as revenue in future periods, was $229 billion as of June 30, 2023, of which $224 billion is related to the commercial portion of revenue. We expect to recognize approximately 45% of this revenue over the next 12 months and the remainder thereafter.</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;, sans-serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:0.0%;font-size:10.0pt;margin-top:0.0pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0.0pt;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <hr style="page-break-after:always;">

// Edgar(tm) Renderer was created by staff of the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission.  Data and content created by government employees within the scope of their employment are not subject to domestic copyright protection. 17 U.S.C. 105.
var Show={};Show.LastAR=null,Show.showAR=function(a,r,w){if(Show.LastAR)Show.hideAR();var e=a;while(e&&e.nodeName!='TABLE')e=e.nextSibling;if(!e||e.nodeName!='TABLE'){var ref=((window)?w.document:document).getElementById(r);if(ref){e=ref.cloneNode(!0);
e.removeAttribute('id');a.parentNode.appendChild(e)}}
if(e)e.style.display='block';Show.LastAR=e};Show.hideAR=function(){Show.LastAR.style.display='none'};Show.toggleNext=function(a){var e=a;while(e.nodeName!='DIV')e=e.nextSibling;if(!e.style){}else if(!e.style.display){}else{var d,p_;if(e.style.display=='none'){d='block';p='-'}else{d='none';p='+'}
e.style.display=d;if(a.textContent){a.textContent=p+a.textContent.substring(1)}else{a.innerText=p+a.innerText.substring(1)}}}

/* Updated 2009-11-04 */
/* v2.2.0.24 */

/* DefRef Styles */

}
